Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.test

Class UnitTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.junit.rules.TestWatcher
      • com.telenav.kivakit.core.test.UnitTest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Receiver<Transmittable>, NamedObject, Listener, Transceiver, org.junit.rules.TestRule
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    KryoUnitTest, WebUnitTest
    public abstract class UnitTest
extends org.junit.rules.TestWatcher
implements Listener
    This is the base test class for all unit tests. It provides useful methods that are common to all tests. Several ensure*() methods delegate to the Ensure class to provide easy access to these methods. A variety of methods provide looping, indexing, iteration and random testing assistance.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
